							"text": "XES3MaP: Explainable Risks Identified from Ensembled Stacked Self-Supervised Models to Augment Predictive Maintenance",
							"articleLocation": "pdfs/CAI2024-2fo5urY39gdhGmFJimhucB/540900b541/540900b541.pdf",
